    • fromCodeOrCustom

      public static HttpStatus fromCodeOrCustom(int code, String description)
      Gets the HttpStatus from the predefined status codes with the code matching the provided code. If there is no predefined HttpStatus a new custom HttpStatus is created.
      Parameters:
      code - the code to find the corresponding HttpStatus
      Returns:
      if found HttpStatus; else a custom HttpStatus from the provided arguments
